      z^n&=\text{cis}{\left(\tfrac{n\theta}{10}\right)} &\hspace{2em} & \tfrac{1}{z}=z^{-n}=\text{cis}{\left(\tfrac{-n\theta}{10}\right)}\\[6pt]
